com.hazelcast.query

Class PartitionPredicate<K,V>

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.hazelcast.query.PartitionPredicate<K,V>
  • Type Parameters:
    K - type of the entry key
    V - type of the entry value
    All Implemented Interfaces:
    DataSerializable, IdentifiedDataSerializable, Predicate<K,V>, Serializable

    public class PartitionPredicate<K,V>
extends Object
implements Predicate<K,V>, IdentifiedDataSerializable
    A Predicate that restricts the execution of a Predicate to a single Partition. This can help to speed up query execution since only a single instead of all partitions needs to be queried. This predicate can only be used as an outer predicate.
